<Objects>
  <!-- Ordinary Client - GATE TO THE UNDERWORLD (Hard dungeon; Egyptian afterlife / the Duat).
       Reconstructed from the aced.gg dev blog (docs/aced-blog/gate-underworld-ra.txt):
       Ra fight = destroy his STAVES first (else later phases brutal) -> sun-channel -> calls the sky
       (Sun Disk + Sun Lasers). Then the Duat boat past the Sun Docks to Sia & Hu. Osiris questline.
       Stats designed; placeholder sprites (chars16x16dEncounters2); reused projectiles. ids 0x8fb0-0x8fb3 + portal 0x820b. -->
